title: 820-3208 not video
message:

title: 820-3208 not video
message:
Do you get 3V at pins 18 & 19 of J9000?
Check in the first few seconds, when the chime sounds.
DP_INT_HPD should go high at same time.

title: 820-3208 not video
message: J9000 pin 18=3v=19. reset pram and gave video display :unsure:why?   It will be that it fails again

message:

Reseting PRAM deleted that error...
